    • Constructor Detail

      • Board

        public Board​(int dimension,
             java.lang.String initialValue,
             java.lang.String hiddenValue,
             boolean initialVisibility)
        Creates the Board object
        Parameters:
        dimension - Side length of board (always square)
        initialValue - Value to fill board with initally, shown when visible - can include color escape sequences, but the printable characters should be 1 character long (chars, emojis, etc.)
        hiddenValue - Value to show when tile is not visible - same as above, printable characters should be 1 charater long
        initialVisibility - State of visibility at beginning - all tiles
